  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:6632:run_test()
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/sanity.sh:15451:main()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="417739" author="adilger" created="Fri, 14 Jun 2024 05:50:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like this test has only failed in the past 6 months when testing patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/55192&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/55192&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17750&quot; title=&quot;kernel update [SLES15 SP4 5.14.21-150400.24.100.2]&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-17750&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-17750&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; kernel: update SLES15 SP4 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;5.14.21-150400.24.100.2&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;:&lt;br/&gt;
